%I A396586 #22 Jun 10 2026 23:55:45
%S A396586 6,15,65,350,2614,18804,187788,1819824,20652336,237005280,3369106080,
%T A396586 44341119360,720135031680,11165392062720,189101097158400,
%U A396586 3359074518374400,68151499873228800,1304266857043046400,29045051171832729600,620314035969116160000
%N A396586 a(n) / (6*n!) is the quadratic moment of the Farey series of order n.
%H A396586 Marko Riedel, <a href="/A396586/a396586_3.pdf">Power moments of the Farey sequence in terms of Bernoulli polynomials and the Jordan totient function</a>
%F A396586 a(n) / (6*n!) = Sum_{r in F_n} r^2 = 1/2 + (1/6)*Sum_{m=1..n} (2*phi(m)+J(m,-1)) where F_n is the Farey sequence on n, phi is the Euler totient and J is the Jordan totient.
%Y A396586 Cf. A006843, A396587.
%K A396586 nonn
%O A396586 1,1
%A A396586 _Marko Riedel_, May 29 2026
